jalse.actions

Class ForkJoinActionEngine

  • java.lang.Object
    • jalse.actions.AbstractActionEngine
      • jalse.actions.ForkJoinActionEngine
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ActionEngine

    public class ForkJoinActionEngine
extends AbstractActionEngine
    An implementation of ActionEngine based on ForkJoinPool. Scheduling is achieved using ForkJoinPool.managedBlock(ManagedBlocker) so many threads may be used but not all executing Action.

    ForkJoinActionEngine offers an instance backed on ForkJoinPool.commonPool() that cannot be stopped or paused (commonPoolEngine()).
    Author:
    Elliot Ford
